name: Sushi Roll
description: A traditional Japanese dish consisting of vinegared rice, seafood, and vegetables rolled in seaweed. Varieties include California roll, spicy tuna roll, and salmon avocado roll.

name: Spaghetti Carbonara
description: A classic Italian pasta dish made with spaghetti, eggs, pancetta, grated cheese, and black pepper. The creamy sauce is created by mixing eggs and cheese with hot pasta.

name: Taco
description: A Mexican dish consisting of a folded or rolled tortilla filled with various ingredients such as beef, chicken, pork, lettuce, cheese, and salsa.

name: Croissant
description: A buttery, flaky pastry originating from France. Made with layers of yeast-leavened dough, butter, and rolled into a crescent shape.

name: Hamburger
description: A classic American dish consisting of a grilled or fried ground meat patty, usually beef, served in a sliced bun with various toppings such as lettuce, tomato, onion, and cheese.

name: Sushi Nigiri
description: Traditional Japanese sushi made with a slice of fresh fish served over a small mound of rice. Common types include tuna, salmon, and shrimp.

name: Pad Thai
description: A popular Thai stir-fried noodle dish made with rice noodles, eggs, tofu, shrimp, bean sprouts, peanuts, and flavored with tamarind sauce.

name: Sushi Sashimi
description: Japanese delicacy consisting of thinly sliced fresh raw fish, served without rice. Common types include tuna, salmon, and yellowtail.

name: Paella
description: A Spanish rice dish originally from Valencia, cooked with saffron, chicken, rabbit, seafood, and various vegetables.

name: Miso Soup
description: A traditional Japanese soup made with dashi stock, miso paste, tofu, seaweed, and green onions. It is usually served as a starter.

name: Peking Duck
description: A famous Chinese dish originating from Beijing, made with roasted duck, served with pancakes, hoisin sauce, cucumber, and green onions.

name: Gelato
description: Italian ice cream made with milk, sugar, and various flavorings. It has a denser and creamier texture than traditional ice cream.
